{"tid":1183940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鏗鏘集: 《八九演義》第五回﹕憶","createTime":"2019-06-03T10:09:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T15:58:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"84aa33eed86e0195817549ae7a8301436582212e","tid":1183940,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T10:09:43.000Z","msg":"03/06/2019<br />\n《八九演義》第五回﹕憶<br />\n1989年6月，中國政府對天安門的抗議學生和民眾清場後，開始通緝參與者，其中包括21名學生領袖。<br />\n通緝令一下，這21名年輕人有的被捕、審判，甚至淪為階下囚，有的則在顛簸中走向自由的國度。30年過去，相中人已年屆半百，人面全非、際遇各異，至今有仍有七人留在中國，其餘都身處海外。《鏗鏘集》記者拿著當年的通緝令，走訪內地、台灣以及美國，遍尋相中人，細聽他們如何守護這段記憶。"},{"pid":"d7c990974450fabcdb02796a643d603c897b0ef0","tid":1183940,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T10:10:55.000Z","msg":"而家TVB做緊,稍後RTHK有重播"},{"pid":"90a38334b667dbd3d8ad2eebd26f8afcd047c0cb","tid":1183940,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T15:58:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U1qjkAyr40o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DU1qjkAyr40o&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOAxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=740eb5f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U1qjkAyr40o</a>"}]}